{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, there cannot exist an entity that crosses the barrier of AGI, even though it may imitate that did so highly effectively.",
    "While AI has made significant advancements in recent years, it still will remain a tool designed to help and augment human intelligence rather than replace it.",
    "It is evident that without human contribution to add information to future datasets, AI capabilities of future models will stall and deteriorate.",
    "Ideally, humans and machines must collaborate in sync, in a beautiful dance, resembling a \"tango of knowledge\" to have mutually beneficial results.",
    "As scientific research continues to unravel the mysteries of both AI and NI, their convergence may reveal the way for new novelties that harness the strengths of both systems, ultimately benefiting our society as a whole."
  ]
}